OL,6,FOne offender, Kevin Lofts, said that
OL,7,Fafter receiving support from the
OL,8,FIntensive Supervision Court, he is
OL,9,Fexcited about his future, as ITV News
OL,10,FUK Editor Paul Brand reports
OL,12,FAn independent review of sentencing
OL,13,Fcommissioned by the government will
OL,14,Ftomorrow recommend scrapping short
OL,15,Fprison sentences, ITV News has
OL,16,Fconfirmed.
