OL,3,CGovernment to be told to scrap short
OL,4,Cprison sentences
OL,6,FThe review has been led by former
OL,7,FConservative Justice Secretary David
OL,8,FGauke, who told us that sentences
OL,9,Funder 12 months do not work and should
OL,10,Fonly be used in exceptional
OL,11,Fcircumstances.
OL,13,FThe Labour government commissioned the
OL,14,Freview amid the overcrowding crisis in
OL,15,Fprisons last year, during which
OL,16,Fthousands of inmates had to be
OL,17,Freleased early.
