OL,3,CGovernment to be told to scrap short
OL,4,Cprison sentences
OL,6,F"There is no real rehabilitation that
OL,7,Fcan get done in prison over that short
OL,8,Fperiod of time. So we would be better
OL,9,Foff in most cases, in most cases,
OL,10,Fworking through the community,
OL,11,Fimposing conditions in the community
OL,12,Fand addressing the underlying causes."
OL,14,FHis review will also recommend
OL,15,Fincentivising inmates to rehabilitate
OL,16,Fby allowing some to be released early
OL,17,Fif they exhibit good behaviour,
OL,18,Fsimilar to the progression-based model
OL,19,Fused by prisons in Texas, USA.
