OL,3,CGovernment to be told to scrap short
OL,4,Cprison sentences
OL,6,F'Good behaviour is rewarded, bad
OL,7,Fbehaviour is punished'
OL,9,F"I think what is important in the
OL,10,Fstructure of a prison sentence is that
OL,11,Fgood behaviour is rewarded, bad
OL,12,Fbehaviour is punished, and that if
OL,13,Fprisoners do stick by the rules, there
OL,14,Fare benefits for them in terms of the
OL,15,Fpoint at which they are released," he
OL,16,Ftold us.
OL,26,@qD@AOU
