OL,3,CGovernment to be told to scrap short
OL,4,Cprison sentences
OL,6,F"And if they don't stick by those
OL,7,Frules, there are consequences as well.
OL,8,FAnd visiting prisons in Texas, I'm
OL,9,Fstruck by how calm they were. There
OL,10,Fwas a greater sense of purpose within
OL,11,Fprisons, and I think part of the
OL,12,Freason for that is the sense of you
OL,13,Fearn progression.
OL,15,F"If you do the right things, you can
OL,16,Fprogress through that sentence."
