OL,6,FThe offenders are asked to take
OL,7,Fregular drug tests and to demonstrate
OL,8,Fhow they are reintegrating into the
OL,9,Fcommunity.
OL,11,FKevin Lofts served 12 years in prison
OL,12,Ffor burglary and theft before instead
OL,13,Fbeing sent to Teesside ISC following
OL,14,Fhis most recent crime.
OL,16,FA lifelong drug addict, he is now in
OL,17,Fthe process of getting clean.
