OL,6,FHe told us prison had left him stuck
OL,7,Fin a cycle of reoffending ` but now,
OL,8,Fafter receiving support from the
OL,9,FIntensive Supervision Court, he is
OL,10,Fexcited about his future.
OL,12,F"Before, I used to spend the best part
OL,13,Fof my day trying to find a score. That
OL,14,Fusually entails me committing a crime,
OL,15,Fburglary, shop theft," he said.
OL,17,F'You used to just tell them what they
OL,18,Fwanted to hear so you could just get
OL,19,Fin get out'
