OL,7,Ffrom probation. I was put along the
OL,8,Fwayside. It was just like you go to
OL,9,Fprobation, they tell you this, that
OL,10,Fand the other and they put you out the
OL,11,Fdoor. You used to just tell them what
OL,12,Fthey wanted to hear so you could just
OL,13,Fget in get out.
