OL,6,F"It's different now with this ISC.
OL,7,FIt's almost like I'm being hand held,
OL,8,Fbut it's not, it's like a big brother
OL,9,Fon your shoulder and that's how it
OL,10,Ffeels, it feels like if you relapse
OL,11,Fand go down old routes, and contact
OL,12,Fthe people you need to they will help
OL,13,Fyou to get back on track and that's
OL,14,Fnever been there before for me."
OL,16,FHe added, "The more you get involved,
OL,17,Fthe more you want to change and do
OL,18,Fbetter for yourself. I think this
OL,19,Fworks."
