OL,6,FIt is too early to release any data
OL,7,Ffrom the trial, but anecdotally, the
OL,8,Fscheme is believed to have cut
OL,9,Freoffending.
OL,11,FChief Inspector Jon Tapper from
OL,12,FCleveland Police told us that he had
OL,13,Fseen "massive changes" in the
OL,14,Fbehaviour of offenders who have
OL,15,Fparticipated in the trial.
OL,26,@uD@FOUuD@VO]
