OL,6,FHe said, "In terms of the individuals
OL,7,Finvolved in the ISC there have been
OL,8,Fmassive changes. So, these people
OL,9,Fcould be classified as career
OL,10,Fcriminals, they've got an extensive
OL,11,Fhistory of crime, lots of convictions,
OL,12,Fwhich results in lots of victims being
OL,13,Fcreated.
OL,15,F"So, we've seen a massive change in
OL,16,Fthe behaviour of those individuals who
OL,17,Fwere impacting the community of
OL,18,FCleveland. Their criminality has
OL,19,Fstopped, and they are starting to make
OL,20,Fa positive contribution to that
OL,21,Fsociety."
