OL,6,FMr Gauke pushed back against
OL,7,Fsuggestions that community sentences
OL,8,Fare softer on criminals, emphasising
OL,9,Fhow a reduction in reoffending will
OL,10,Falso reduce the number of victims of
OL,11,Fcrime in the longer term.
OL,13,F'There's really very strong
OL,14,Foptimism... we'll have a tagging
OL,15,Fsystem that is working properly'
