OL,3,CGovernment to be told to scrap short
OL,4,Cprison sentences
OL,6,FHe told ITV News, "There will be fewer
OL,7,Fwho will go to prison. But I think the
OL,8,Fpoint I would make here is what most
OL,9,Fvictims would want is to ensure that
OL,10,Fthere are fewer crimes in future, that
OL,11,Fthere are fewer victims.
OL,13,F"And we do have to ask ourselves what
OL,14,Fis going to be the most effective way
OL,15,Fin which we can address that? And yes,
OL,16,Fpunishment is important and prison is
OL,17,Fimportant, but they're not the only
OL,18,Fparts of the criminal justice system.
OL,26,@nD@SOU
