OL,3,CGovernment to be told to scrap short
OL,4,Cprison sentences
OL,6,F"And the criminal justice system as a
OL,7,Fwhole has got to be really effective
OL,8,Fin ensuring that if you've got a
OL,9,Fcriminal, they stop committing crimes
OL,10,Fin the future."
OL,12,FGauke also told us his report will
OL,13,Frecommend the tagging system is
OL,14,Fimproved, with recent reports that
OL,15,Foffenders have gone untagged for
OL,16,Fmonths after being released from jail.
