OL,6,F"There clearly have been problems with
OL,7,Fhow the tagging system has operated,
OL,8,Fbut as we're moving into that
OL,9,Fimplementation stage, we know that
OL,10,Fthese are issues that can be addressed.
OL,12,F"There has been progress on that.
OL,13,FThere's really very strong optimism
OL,14,Fthat by the time our recommendations
OL,15,Fare put in place, we'll have a tagging
OL,16,Fsystem that is working properly."
OL,18,F'The probation system as a whole needs
OL,19,Fto be properly funded to be able to
