OL,6,FHe also said his report will recommend
OL,7,Fan increase in funding for the
OL,8,Fprobation service.
OL,10,F"I think there's a really important
OL,11,Fpoint that as we try to control the
OL,12,Fprison population, which we have to
OL,13,Fdo, there's no escaping that it will
OL,14,Fshift prisoners' pressures elsewhere.
OL,16,F"And our report, when you see it
OL,17,Ftomorrow, will be very strong in the
OL,18,Frecommendations that we make, that the
OL,19,Fprobation system as a whole needs to
OL,20,Fbe properly funded to be able to deal
OL,21,Fwith this."
